      • providers

        public List<String> providers()
        Gets the providers. Select a provider. Supported values are `ghost` and `ims`. To list GhoST tags and infrastructure tags use `ghost,ims`. `service` tags can only be attached to GhoST onboarded resources, so you don't need to set this parameter when listing `service` tags.
        Returns:
        the providers

      • attachedTo

        public String attachedTo()
        Gets the attachedTo. If you want to return only the list of tags attached to a specified resource, pass the ID of the resource on this parameter. For GhoST onboarded resources, the resource ID is the CRN; for IMS resources, it is the IMS ID. When using this parameter, you must specify the appropriate provider (`ims` or `ghost`).

        the attachedTo
